               <p>JOHN STANLEY. I am a <rs id="t18270531-214-viclabel1139" type="occupation">carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-214-victim1191 t18270531-214-viclabel1139"></join>. On the 11th of April I lost these tools from a shop in <placeName id="t18270531-214-crimeloc1140">Northampton-row, Holloway</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270531-214-crimeloc1140" type="placeName" value="Northampton-row, Holloway"></interp>
