                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-214-off1137 t18270531-214-crimeloc1140"></join> - I locked up the shop, and a desk which was in it, about seven o'clock; I was called up next morning. about half-past five, by Taylor, and found the prisoner at the watch-house with them.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270531-214-person1192">
                  THOMAS 
                  TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t18270531-214-person1192" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
